<dl id="n05075p"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05075p">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05075p"> 75(p)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> large money</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">It is said that the terrified watch went and told the chief priests and elders, who gave them &ldquo;<mark>large money</mark>,&rdquo; and asked them to say the disciples came by night and stole the body <font color="green">[of Jesus]</font> whilst they slept, and promised to make it all right with Pilate. <small> G.W. Foote, <a name="BROM" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#BROM"><cite title="source">Bible Romances</cite></a>, 4th ed. (1922) [The Ressurection] 212</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: See also <a name="n05021c" href="n05all.htm#n05021c">N05 (VI.B.2):021(c)</a></mm> </dd></dl>
